Source: turbine
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Turbine Contributors <turbine@example.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), cargo, rustc (>= 1.75)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://github.com/turbine-queue/turbine
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: turbine-server
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: redis-server | rabbitmq-server
Description: Turbine task queue server
 High-performance distributed task queue written in Rust.
 This package contains the Turbine server component that
 coordinates task distribution and manages queues.

Package: turbine-worker
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: turbine-server
Description: Turbine task queue worker
 High-performance distributed task queue written in Rust.
 This package contains the Turbine worker component that
 executes tasks from the queue.

Package: turbine-dashboard
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: turbine-server
Description: Turbine web dashboard
 High-performance distributed task queue written in Rust.
 This package contains the Turbine web dashboard for
 monitoring tasks and workers.

Package: turbine
Architecture: any
Depends: turbine-server (= ${binary:Version}),
         turbine-worker (= ${binary:Version}),
         turbine-dashboard (= ${binary:Version}),
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: Turbine task queue (metapackage)
 High-performance distributed task queue written in Rust.
 This is a metapackage that installs all Turbine components.
